# Vercel function build artifact — the bundled api/index.js is committed
# as a placeholder (vercel.json's `functions` config is parsed BEFORE the
# buildCommand runs, so the file must exist at deploy time). esbuild
# overwrites the placeholder during deploy with the real handler. The
# sourcemap is purely a build artifact and stays ignored.
api/index.js.map
